queries.sql:
select concat (ui.name, " ",ui.lastname) as "Nombre Completo", ui.birthday,
	ui.phone, p.title, p.status
	from userinfo as ui
	join users as u
	on ui.id= u.id
	join posts as p
	on p.autor= ui.id 
	where p.status=0 limit 100;
